{
  "text": "Some previous meta-analyses observed a significant positive effect of non-surgical periodontal treatment on glycemic control despite lack of homogeneity and robustness among studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Since then, some new randomized controlled trials have been done. Therefore, it is time to provide an update to accumulate more evidence and evaluate the potential effect of non-surgical periodontal treatment on glycemic control. ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "45755794",
